{
  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 10,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Authority pipeline (meter **ArchLucid**)\n\nStable names match **`docs/library/OBSERVABILITY.md`** (source **`ArchLucidInstrumentation.cs`**).\n\n| Signal | What good looks like | Alert rule |\n|--------|---------------------|-------------|\n| **`archlucid_authority_pipeline_work_pending`** | Well **below 50** for normal load | **`ArchLucidAuthorityPipelineWorkBacklog`**: **`> 50`** for **15m** |\n| **`archlucid_authority_pipeline_work_oldest_pending_age_seconds`** | Seconds near zero | **`ArchLucidAuthorityPipelineWorkStale`**: **`> 3600`** for **20m** |\n| **`archlucid_data_consistency_*_total`** | Zero **`rate`** in steady state | **`ArchLucidDataConsistencyOrphansDetected`** / **`ArchLucidDataConsistencyAlertsRaised`** ( **`1h`** windows in **`infra/prometheus/archlucid-alerts.yml`** ) |\n\n**Import:** Grafana → **Dashboards** → **Import** → upload this JSON → bind variable **`${datasource}`** to **Prometheus**. Optional Terraform root: **`infra/terraform-monitoring/grafana_dashboards.tf`**. Runbook **`docs/runbooks/AUTHORITY_PIPELINE_OBSERVABILITY.md`** (clone).",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Meter / alert alignment",
      "transparent": false,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "description": "Histogram **`archlucid_authority_pipeline_stage_duration_ms`** — labels **`stage`**, **`outcome`** per **`OBSERVABILITY.md`**. If empty, confirm OTLP histogram export names (`*_bucket`) on scrape.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "decimals": 1, "unit": "ms" },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 7 },
      "id": 11,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(archlucid_authority_pipeline_stage_duration_ms_bucket[5m])) by (le, stage, outcome))",
          "legendFormat": "{{stage}} {{outcome}} p95",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Pipeline stage duration (p95 per stage/outcome)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "description": "Observable gauge depth on **`dbo.AuthorityPipelineWorkOutbox`**. **Yellow / red shading** approximates Prometheus **`ArchLucidAuthorityPipelineWorkBacklog`** (>50 for **15m**).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 40 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 50 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 16 },
      "id": 12,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "archlucid_authority_pipeline_work_pending",
          "legendFormat": "pending rows",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Authority outbox backlog (gauge)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "description": "Oldest unprocessed **`AuthorityPipelineWorkOutbox`** row age. Prometheus **`ArchLucidAuthorityPipelineWorkStale`** at **>3600s** (**20m** **`for`**). Increase worker replicas when persistently elevated + SQL tier is healthy.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 2700 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 3600 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 16 },
      "id": 13,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "archlucid_authority_pipeline_work_oldest_pending_age_seconds",
          "legendFormat": "oldest age",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Oldest pending age (authority outbox)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "description": "Detection-only orphans vs **`ArchLucidDataConsistencyOrphansDetected`**; **`alerts_total`** vs **`ArchLucidDataConsistencyAlertsRaised`**; **`orphans_quarantined_total`** when quarantine mode inserts rows. Alerts use **`1h`** `rate`; panel uses **`5m`** for responsiveness — widen if noisy.",
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 24 },
      "id": 14,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(archlucid_data_consistency_orphans_detected_total[5m])) by (table)",
          "legendFormat": "orphans/s {{table}}",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(archlucid_data_consistency_alerts_total[5m])) by (table)",
          "legendFormat": "alert signal/s {{table}}",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(archlucid_data_consistency_orphans_quarantined_total[5m])) by (table)",
          "legendFormat": "quarantined/s {{table}}",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Data consistency: orphans vs alerts vs quarantine (rates)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "s" },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 32 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(traces_span_latency_bucket{span_name=~\"authority\\\\.(context_ingestion|graph|findings|decisioning|artifacts)\"}[5m])) by (le, span_name))",
          "legendFormat": "{{span_name}} p95",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Authority stage span latency (OTel traces, p95)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 32 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(increase(traces_span_count{span_name=\"AuthorityRun\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Authority runs (5m)",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Authority run throughput (OTel spans)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "description": "Meter **ArchLucid** counters. Empty series ⇒ confirm Prometheus scrape translates histogram/counter names (OTLP mapping version).",
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 40 },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(archlucid_authority_runs_completed_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "authority runs completed / s",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Authority runs completed (app counter)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 40 },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (agent_type_key, outcome) (rate(archlucid_agent_handler_invocations_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{agent_type_key}} {{outcome}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Agent handler invocations (by type)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 48 },
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(archlucid_llm_prompt_tokens_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "prompt tokens/s",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(archlucid_llm_completion_tokens_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "completion tokens/s",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "LLM token rates (Azure OpenAI completions)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "tags": ["archlucid", "authority", "authority-pipeline", "prometheus"],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "current": {},
        "hide": 0,
        "label": "Datasource",
        "name": "datasource",
        "options": [],
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "regex": "",
        "type": "datasource"
      }
    ]
  },
  "time": { "from": "now-6h", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "browser",
  "title": "ArchLucid — Authority pipeline",
  "uid": "archlucid-authority",
  "version": 2,
  "weekStart": ""
}
